---------------------------------------------------------------------------

by keradus at 2016-05-21T16:23:45Z

> Is `@param str` a valid phpdoc type?

Yes, it's valid phpdoc type.

```php
class str {}

/**
 * @param str $s
 */
function (str $s) {}
```

